         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, 3/8/74 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ At a meeting of the Trustees of the Royal Park, held this day, it was reported that the Brahmin cow in the zoologic reserve had been killed by ferocious dogs, and that als...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">74.08.03</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Frederick Standish</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A345 Royal Park<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Trustees<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>letter &amp; minute book, p. 58, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, 3/8/74</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>At a meeting of the Trustees of the Royal Park, held this day, it was reported that the Brahmin cow in the zoologic reserve had been killed by ferocious dogs, and that also a grazing cow had been injured. My colleagues desired me to bring these occurrences and the frequent invasion of the Park by dogs not under any control of visitors, to the notice of your department, and to solicit that you would kindly afford such protection through the local police force, as circumstances may permit, especially as there is even danger to human life, if large and ferocious dogs are allowed by their owners to roam about unchecked.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your very obedient</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hon. Secr. T. R. P.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Trustees Royal Park.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Capt. Standish</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Chief Commissioner of Police.</p>
